title: Do not use!
text: I moved across the country and this map application made it completely horrible. It didn‚Äôt know about a major bridge closure and it took me through extensive construction areas, it had me drive to Virginia through little town roads in Kentucky through insane mountain twists and turns instead of using highways and interstate roads. Twice it had me turn off the road I was on to take another road and then had me turn around and go back to the road I was on. A move and a cross country drive are stressful enough without a map app that makes it as miserable as possible. I wonder if the developers thought this was a fun joke. I deleted google maps from all of my devices and I want to warn others.
